---
// 终端彩蛋弹窗：监听 open-easter-egg 事件显示，并触发 confetti 反馈（canvas-confetti 已装）
---
<div class="egg-overlay" id="easterEggOverlay" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="egg-card">
    <button class="egg-close" id="easterEggClose" aria-label="关闭">&times;</button>
    <div class="egg-content">
      <div class="ee-diamond">&#9670;</div>
      <p class="ee-title">我终于活成了自己讨厌的样子</p>
      <p class="ee-text">
        小时候总以为长大就能拥有全世界，<br />
        后来才发现，长大只是学会了接受失去。<br /><br />
        那些深夜写下又删掉的朋友圈，<br />
        那些话到嘴边又咽回去的瞬间，<br />
        那些明明很委屈却笑着说「没事」的日子——<br />
        我们不是在长大，我们只是在学会伪装。<br /><br />
        十八岁那年我以为自己是主角，<br />
        二十五岁发现自己顶多是个龙套，<br />
        跑龙套的工资还经常被拖欠。<br /><br />
        这个世界教会我的第一课不是善良，<br />
        是闭嘴。<br />
        第二课不是奋斗，<br />
        是认命。<br /><br />
        我花了好多年才明白一个道理：<br />
        有些人光是活着，就已经用尽了全部力气。<br />
        而我就是那个「有些人」。
      </p>
      <div class="ee-divider"></div>
      <p class="ee-signature">— 如果这就是人生的答案，那我宁愿没答过这道题</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .egg-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 2000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(10, 10, 20, 0.72);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: opacity 0.35s ease, visibility 0.35s;
  }
  .egg-overlay.open {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
  }
  .egg-card {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 86vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 2.6rem 2rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.96);
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
  }
  .egg-overlay.open .egg-card {
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
  }
  .egg-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem;
    right: 1.2rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .egg-close:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .ee-diamond {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ee-title {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-blue), var(--accent-purple), var(--accent-cyan));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ee-text {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-align: left;
  }
  .ee-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
    margin: 1.4rem 0;
  }
  .ee-signature {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-align: right;
  }
</style>

<script>
  import confetti from 'canvas-confetti';

  const overlay = document.getElementById('easterEggOverlay');
  const close = document.getElementById('easterEggClose');

  function open() {
    overlay?.classList.add('open');
    overlay?.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'false');
    confetti({ particleCount: 120, spread: 70, origin: { y: 0.6 } });
  }
  function hide() {
    overlay?.classList.remove('open');
    overlay?.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
  }

  window.addEventListener('open-easter-egg', open);
  close?.addEventListener('click', hide);
  overlay?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    if (e.target === overlay) hide();
  });
  window.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Escape' && overlay?.classList.contains('open')) hide();
  });
</script>
